00:28:27,916 --> 00:28:29,316
and this service is the one


611
00:28:29,316 --> 00:28:31,626
where you actually
associate a particular license


612
00:28:31,656 --> 00:28:34,076
with a particular user
effectively assigning it


613
00:28:34,816 --> 00:28:36,016
to them.


614
00:28:36,206 --> 00:28:38,616
Provide some information
including the secure token,


615
00:28:39,366 --> 00:28:42,536
call the service, and then the
response might look something


616
00:28:42,536 --> 00:28:44,746
like this where you get
some additional details


617
00:28:44,746 --> 00:28:47,196
about the license that's been
assigned including its ID,


