00:29:20,946 --> 00:29:22,886
to invite users to
link to the program.


632
00:29:25,906 --> 00:29:28,596
There's a service that will
allow you to get all the details


633
00:29:28,596 --> 00:29:31,616
about a specific user including
any licenses currently assigned


634
00:29:31,616 --> 00:29:32,176
to that user.


635
00:29:33,416 --> 00:29:35,096
You can of course get
a list of all the users


