00:40:53,576 --> 00:40:55,836
from both the organization
and the end user perspective.


871
00:40:56,306 --> 00:40:57,106
So what's the workflow


872
00:40:57,106 --> 00:40:59,276
for an organization now
using this new service?


873
00:40:59,886 --> 00:41:01,826
Well, they hopefully
order lots and lots


874
00:41:01,826 --> 00:41:03,666
of Apple devices from us.


