00:44:06,826 --> 00:44:08,666
and it again breaks
down to three areas.


944
00:44:09,496 --> 00:44:13,056
Similar account authentication
to the new App Store VPP.


945
00:44:13,056 --> 00:44:16,666
You'll need to create a settings
editor for that small handful


946
00:44:16,666 --> 00:44:17,406
of settings for the--


947
00:44:17,406 --> 00:44:18,716
your customers to be able


